
This script will get product details from beautypedia.

I- REQUIREMENTS

II- DESCRIPTION

	-pro_beautypedia.py: to get the product detail and all the review of this product

III- INPUT

	- No need input	

IV-OUTPUT

	- product.json: list all product details in beautypedia
	- product_review.json: list all review (comment) of that product

V- HOW TO RUN IT

1. Open terminal and go to your directory.
2. Launch the script python pro_beautypedia.py

